{"tid":1041834,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(壞harddisk) 部份raw檔recovery失敗，求高手。","createTime":"2019-03-01T06:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T16:55:01.000Z","uid":113250,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0655c3de9725aa7c47cf0100f864fc7fb93bea8","tid":1041834,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"本身用Toshiba 3T x2,<br />\nSynology 218play NAS, 行raid 1.<br />\n9成都係相，Nikon NEF RAW，D810，Z6<br />\n<br />\n事情：<br />\n有日過相入到一半話full左，cancel完重開NAS，話missing harddisk，status light 橙燈，同埋見到有一個disk light無著。<br />\n<br />\n我跟官方guidelines，熄機重新入harddisk，rebuild DSM. 但rebuild完果下都話失敗，找不到硬碟。<br />\n<br />\nRecovery過程：<br />\n買左個新harddisk box (Akitio), 直插兩個HDD，電腦有連接既提示聽，但&ldquo;My computer&quot;無顯示。另外插左個舊HDD就有show到。<br />\n<br />\n因為廢是試壞兩個HDD, 之後我淨係試一個。喺disk management睇到幾個partition healthy, 2個unlocated.<br />\n<br />\n然後就用左個paid software (Stellar Photo Recovery), 去scan左個6個鐘，然後recover入左個新既WD red 4TB，結果係睇得返d810既NEF, JPG, MP4, etc.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問題：<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">有關於Nikon Z6既NEF RAW file完全搵唔到, 而且有~400GB .PPM file (portable pixmap format )被recovered, 每個都係10MB.</span> <br />\n<br />\n我上Reddit搵過話有機會係false positive, 但我又諗緊會唔會係fragmented NEF files?<br />\n<br />\n然後我直接問Stellar嘅technician係唔係支援Z6 raw format, 佢就咁答：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYkUziF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYkUziF.jpg&h=b3b4d6d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我應該用埋deep scan, 定係直接放棄俾人整算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb619990219376704d4c5d8261bf6260facde4c2","tid":1041834,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"上維修公司：<br />\n由於我分開左兩個harddisk, 一其中一個harddisk我無scan過無點整過。所以我就喺scan緊一個HDD既時候，就拎左另一個無scan過既HDD上維修公司（荔枝角）。佢好快check完就話係壞磁頭，要入lab整，開價$7800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n咁而加就等埋屋企果個scan完，拎埋去睇，斷估唔會又壞埋個磁頭咁黑仔掛。但正常無壞磁頭都要收$2000up.<br />\n<br />\n所以想問問想樣先可以找返我Z6啲raw<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明都行raid1嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc5599850ab057d9b75765b55e60e53957b38d8","tid":1041834,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"我知道連登咩高手都有嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cd0585c653a98883597d90a9eb46d948540ba3","tid":1041834,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"精簡問題：<br />\n- 點解舊既D810可以拎返raw但新既Z6唔得？<br />\n- 果啲PPM (10MB/file) 可唔可以recovery成NEF?<br />\n- 再scan落去會唔會死埋個HDD?"},{"pid":"235f1b068483a05b9ddf1227dd82a2980ff25a79","tid":1041834,"uid":56497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30cd0585c653a98883597d90a9eb46d948540ba3","tid":1041834,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"精簡問題：<br />\n- 點解舊既D810可以拎返raw但新既Z6唔得？<br />\n- 果啲PPM (10MB/file) 可唔可以recovery成NEF?<br />\n- 再scan落去會唔會死埋個HDD?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T07:08:10.000Z","msg":"你試下用testdisk, 我之前壞SD卡都係用佢救番我D RAW檔出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cgsecurity.org/wiki/TestDisk_Download\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cgsecurity.org%2Fwiki%2FTestDisk_Dow